# Repository layout

This repository uses the explicit monorepo layout recorded by Copier.

## Package map

| Package | Slug | Path | Profiles | Check task |
|---|---|---|---|---|
[% for package in monorepo_packages %]| [[ package.display_name | replace('|', '\\|') ]] | `[[ package.slug ]]` | `[[ package.path ]]` | `[[ package.language_profiles | join(', ') ]]` | `//[[ package.path ]]:check` |
[% endfor %]

The root `mise.toml` owns the union of tool versions, aggregate tasks, and the only `mise.lock`.
`scripts/setup-tooling.py` is the only lock, locked-install, and hook authority. Package `mise.toml` files own task
commands and execute from their package roots; they do not declare tools.

`mise run check` validates every declared package plus shared repository policy. Pre-commit and `mise run fix` use hk
file globs, so package source checks are selected by changed package paths while shared documentation and workflow files
continue to use root policy.
